OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FFurther scattered showers,
OL,6,Fwith patchy rain at times across the
OL,7,FPennines. Best chance of brighter
OL,8,Fspells in the east. A brisk breeze but
OL,9,Ffeeling milder.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FThursday, cloud and rain easing north
OL,13,Fthen drier, warmer. Friday, warm with
OL,14,Fbright or sunny spells. Chance of
OL,15,Fthundery evening showers. Saturday,
OL,16,Fwarm with bright spells, thundery
OL,17,Fshowers still possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
